body:
FlatUIColorSwatches
===================

Colors from www.flatuicolors.com as an installable Photoshop swatch

Just clone the repo and double click on the .aco to add them to Photoshop

Or.... click [here](https://github.com/brianmichel/FlatUIColorSwatches/raw/master/FlatUIColors.aco) to download directly
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
